        "Description": "Good afternoon 47,\r\ryour target is group of professional, retired marines called The Elite Masks. This group is connected for being hired as professional assassins, personal bodyguards and private mercenaries. What makes them our targtets, is that one of our clients was a victim of an attack on his private villa in 2021, where Elite Masks eliminated everyone on the site and stole 10 000 000€ artifact. Client seeks a revenge and wants us to eliminate them as soon as possible.\r\rGood luck agent.",
